        </div>
        <div class="container">
            <h1><span class="gradient-text">💀 Memory Management Vibes 💀</span></h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Never worry about memory again, bestie!</p>
            <div class="alert-box">
                <h4>⚠️ Deprecated Documentation</h4>
                <p>This documentation page is deprecated. Please use <a href="garbage_collection.html">the updated version</a> instead.</p>
